					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"So that’s why she was so upset when she was close to being expelled from the island and separated from all of her friends...",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"所以，当快要被赶出岛、和伙伴们分开的时候，她才这么心灰意冷⋯⋯",
